    {
      "instruction": "<p>Combine your <strong>tamari soy sauce</strong> and <strong>chopped garlic</strong> in a bowl with the juice of <strong>half</strong> your <strong>lime[s]</strong>, your <strong>sesame oil</strong>, a pinch of <strong>salt </strong>and 1 tbsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[1 1/2 tbsp]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[2 tbsp]</span><strong> sugar</strong></p><p>Give it a good mix up – this is your <strong>South Asian-style dressing</strong></p>",
      "order": 3,
