    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the curried meat-free chicken<strong> </strong>has browned, add your <strong>roasted peanuts</strong> and <strong>toasted sesame seeds</strong> to the pan and cook for 1-2 min or until fragrant and lightly toasted – this is your <strong>curried meat-free chicken </strong>and<strong> peanuts & sesame</strong></p>",
