      "instruction": "<p>Once the rice is cooked, add the<strong> tomato wedges</strong>, <strong>shredded lettuce</strong> and <strong>carrot ribbons</strong> to the pot and gently stir it all together</p><p>Add the <strong>South Asian-style dressing</strong> and <strong>chopped coriander</strong> and give everything a good mix up – this is your <strong>South Asian-style</strong> <strong>rice salad</strong></p>",
